# Architecture rules

Target architecture: modular monolith.

Preferred backend layering:
- views: HTTP layer
- serializers: request/response validation
- services: business actions and writes
- selectors: read/query logic
- validators: reusable business validation
- tasks: async/background work

Do not introduce microservices.
Do not introduce event-driven complexity unless explicitly requested.
Do not rewrite full domains in one step.
For large files, extract one business capability at a time.